overview: Air Thugger stands in the middle of a trashed living room. He's a frat pledge who has been tasked with getting the place cleaned up while the others are out. As Thugger starts cleaning, there's a knock on the front door. He answers it to reveal Lolly Dames, a stunningly hot maid who was sent to help him. As she works, Lolly talks about how she used to get up to TONS of wild stuff when she was in college. Lolly invites Thugger to do whatever he wants to her, and Thugger is happy to oblige!  It's a busy day at Adira Allure's massage parlor. Luckily for her, her first client is Milan, who just happens to be her favorite! Adira calls Milan into the private massage room and has him strip down to his underwear and lie on the table. As Adira begins massaging Milan, she starts getting turned on by his muscular body.
title: Not Your Typical Maid
